#
# RVE (R Virtual Environment)
#

1) run "source ~/RVE/bin/activate"

- The prompt changed (welcome aboard!)
- Your HOME directory is now ~/RVE.
- Your PATH add "bin/" and you'll be able to run R
- You'll find a basic ".Rprofile" in your HOME.
- The "workspace/" directory should be used for your code.

2) run "deactivate"

- HOME and PATH vars will be restored to previous setup.
